        I survived the crash, survived Jensen and Reed dying to save me, survived losing SAM—and now I'm going to die because my AI replacement wants to teach me about cellular respiration while I'm actively bleeding.

        But also… it's so absurd, so completely, ridiculously absurd that a laugh tries to escape—it hurts my ribs.

